cle></div></div></div></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1741843-20240226.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://cyberdefender.hk/scameter/">Cyber Defender</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/scameter-new-app-auto-distinguish-scam-call-and-web/life-tech/smartcity/">防騙視伏 APP 升級版可識別詐騙來電及網站，警方強調：不會儲存紀錄</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
