            <title>新 Tesla Model 3 Plaid 版西班牙曝光，疑似配備 Ludicrous Mode</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/new-tesla-model-3-plaid/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-tesla-model-3-plaid</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/new-tesla-model-3-plaid/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 07:35:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 Plaid]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221261</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前網友 @dessiewisley 在 X （前稱 Twitter）表示在西班牙華倫西亞看見 Tesla Model 3 Plaid 版本，車尾更有一個意義不明的新徽章。@SawyerMerritt 表示這個徽章象徵是次曝光的 Tesla Model 3 具有「Ludicrous Mode」，這個模式之前在 2016-2021 的 Tesla Model S 及 Model X 的 Performance 版本出現過。</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">New model 3 Plaid being Filmed in Valencia Spain <a href="https://twitter.com/garyblack00?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@garyblack00</a><a href="https://twitter.com/WholeMarsBlog?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@WholeMarsBlog</a><a href="https://twitter.com/Teslaconomics?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Teslaconomics</a><a href="https://twitter.com/teslaownersirl?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@teslaownersirl</a><a href="https://t.co/N1du5ERjoy">pic.twitter.com/N1du5ERjoy</a></p>&mdash; Desmond Wisley (@dessiewisley) <a href="https://twitter.com/dessiewisley/status/1761795423822323939?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 25, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲懷疑象徵「Ludicrous Mode」的新徽章</p><p>雖然上圖的徽章驟眼看起來和 Plaid 版本相近，但據 @SawyerMerritt 表示，上圖的徽章實際上象徵著「Ludicrous Mode」。據 Tesla 官方網站資料顯示，Ludicrous Mode 下的 Model S 能夠將峯值扭力增加約 60%（適用於配備 Ludicrous 升級的 Performance 版全輪驅動車輛）。</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Nope <a href="https://t.co/2SFGZHZeaO">pic.twitter.com/2SFGZHZeaO</a></p>&mdash; Sawyer Merritt (@SawyerMerritt) <a href="https://twitter.com/SawyerMerritt/status/1761803972619473071?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 25, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708923404-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708923404-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708923404.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>據 @SawyerMerritt 表示，早前在西班牙曝光的 Model 3 Performance （Ludicrous）配備 Performance 座位，而且車身懸掛更低，以及使用代表高性能的紅色煞車鉗。</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">BREAKING: New Model 3 Performance (Ludicrous) spotted for the first time fully uncovered.<br><br>Initial noticeable differences vs LR:<br>• Performance seats<br>• Wheels (aero caps)<br>• Red brake calipers<br>• Front splitter<br>• Ludicrous badge on rear<br>• Lowered suspension<br>• Rear spoiler… <a href="https://t.co/kBjWULR98T">https://t.co/kBjWULR98T</a></p>&mdash; Sawyer Merritt (@SawyerMerritt) <a href="https://twitter.com/SawyerMerritt/status/1761802489626521930?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 25, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/dessiewisley/status/1761795423822323939">dessiewisley@X</a>、<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/teslamotors/comments/1aztqak/possible_new_tesla_highland_model_3/?rdt=47293">r/teslamotors@Reddit</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/tesla-employee-train-giga-berlin/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">為方便員工往返超級工廠   Tesla 德國收購鐵路提供免費列車服務</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/cybertruck-4/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">YouTuber 駕 Cyber​​truck 落河未有死火　Tesla：如有損壞保險不包</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/tesla-model-3-highland-performance-spy-photos/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla Model 3 改版新成員   Performance 版諜照曝光內設跑車桶椅</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/new-tesla-model-3-plaid/life-tech/auto/">新 Tesla Model 3 Plaid 版西班牙曝光，疑似配備 Ludicrous Mode</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
